definition: Loongson (a family of general-purpose CPUs developed within China)

sentences.english: Loongson could also reshape the global PC business.
sentences.chinese: 龍芯也可能改變全球計算機產業格局。

sentences.english: The Loongson processor is based on the MIPS instruction set, the basic commands that a microprocessor understands.
sentences.chinese: 龍芯基於MIPS指令集，屬於精簡的指令集。
